---
title: Chorizo Poutine with Fresh Salad
description: Poutine is an absolute Quebec classic and tonight's version is sure to show you the mere possibilities this iconic dish has to offer. This poutine is so good, you'd swear you were sitting in Parc La Fontaine taking in the fresh air!
